{"tid":36492,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨　陳浩天周浩輝　在台灣　遭　愛字頭組織　襲擊","createTime":"2016-12-12T17:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T17:31:29.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0604e846e6d7ae5ef919a85b6fc9a61a330676a9","tid":36492,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F580288865503405&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f69f2303\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405</a><br />\n<br />\n【召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝於台灣遇襲】<br />\n敝黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝今日(12/12)晚上於台北一餐廳接受記者訪問後，當二人準備離開餐廳，多人即衝前施襲，並在場高叫「搞港獨台獨」、「漢奸賣國」。民族黨強烈譴責施襲者及其背後相關團體。二人並無大礙，現於台北中正區一警察局錄取口供，稍後將進一步交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.580288865503405%2F580288148836810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c56681e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/pcb.580288865503405/580288148836810/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/fQ9mga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfQ9mga&h=aac709e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWilliam Liang:<br />\n這個就是愛國同心會的張秀葉，嫁來台灣，鼓吹統一，常在101拿五星旗鬧事打人。"},{"pid":"ae3de9a819c3e71f026488b1ffaf684c28807534","tid":36492,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}